$ Perl module Net::FTP: logging in with Net::Netrc

gh|PerlModules|/Net/FTP/login-with-Net-Netrc.pl||

`Net::Netrc` seems to also work on → Windows if there is a → Linux/fhs/home/username/_netrc[`.netrc`] file in → Windows/dirs/Users/username[`C:\users\username`].

